<p>A. Platt Articles</p><p> B. Political Correspondence</p><p> C. Drugstore Correspondence</p><p> D. Newspapers</p><p> E. Miscellaneous Correspondence</p><p> F. Local History</p><p> G. Pamphlets and Broadsides.</p>  </arrangement>
